Florence C. CASLER et al., Appellants, v. R. E. ALLEN, as Trustee in Bankruptcy of LLOYD & CASLER, Inc., a Corporation, Bankrupt, Appellee. No. 6176. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 26, 1930.

Before RUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
